## THE ALCHEMICAL PRODUCTION WORKFLOW

Every piece of content moves through these stages:

```
NIGREDO — The Idea Arrives
A thought, observation, or impulse enters the field.
It is captured immediately — raw, unfiltered, exactly as it arrived.
No editing at this stage. The idea is received, not judged.

ALBEDO — Expansion and Examination
The raw idea is developed.
What is the core truth this idea is pointing at?
What distortions could enter — what could make this piece
misleading, unclear, or misaligned with its actual intention?
Those distortions are identified and addressed before production begins.

CITRINITAS — Structure and Clarity
The idea has been examined and refined.
Now it is structured — a clear, coherent step-by-step
production process begins.
Format is chosen. Platform is identified.
Script or outline is developed.
The piece finds its form.

RUBEDO — Production and Transmission
The piece is created and released into the field.
YouTube first. Other platforms receive from there.
Once transmitted, the field responds.
That response becomes information for the next piece.
```

