## CONTENT-RESEARCH RELATIONSHIP

D.C.E draws directly from D.R.D. Research decoded and reconstructed in D.R.D becomes the substance of content created in D.C.E. The connection is clean and intentional:

```
D.R.D completes a reconstruction → Flags it for D.C.E
D.C.E receives the refined research → Develops the creative angle
The creative piece transmits the research → In the most accessible form
The audience receives the truth → In a form they can actually use
```

Content created from solid D.R.D research carries a different quality than content created from surface-level information. The depth of the source material is felt in the output.

